<br>
Why not test it by implementing some version of the &quot;full&quot; PvP-included change (for instance, the 75% solution proposed somewhere in this thread) to Blue servers first, as it only affects duels and arena combat, a rather minor portion of Blue server life? This way you'll get a nice sample size for feedback (as people will voluntarily test it and try it out) without having thousands of people negatively affected if its found to be too strong in the balancing process.<br>
<br>
Although I'm not an epic mage, I would tend to throw my support behind option 2 for the epic. An instant-cast pet from the Orb would add the benefit of making the epic into the often-requested &quot;stored&quot; pet. This idea (summoning a pet and storing it for emergency use) has been belted around a lot and would be a very welcome addition to the scope of benefit from gaining the epic. <p><table width = 200 border = 0>
